    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Ajio - Apply Now",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Ajio. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Marketplace Manager to strengthen our Chandigarh-based team.\n\nAbout Ajio:\nAjio is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chandigarh, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ajio!",
